      "id": "5a93c517_ae2a1f8e",
      "file_path": "pgaas/pgaas/logginginterface.py",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 28,
      "message": "The log record being written as \"msg\" to the log file is incomplete.  The ctx.logger.* methods provide important additional information when they write a record--like the node instance, the operation that's being performed, etc.   The log file is also incomplete because it does not contain the records dropped by the Cloudify process that's calling into the plugin.  In short, the log file that's being written here is of extremely limited value.",
